                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, M</hi> 145). I took the prisoner, and told the charge—she denied it, and said she was at a public-house at the time.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never saw the. man till the Sunday night.</p>
